                             How to play game?
                             -----------------

        On  level  1, find generator, go near it, and destroy it.  You will
need  keys,  marked with numbers to enter teleport room which will teleport
you  to  generator room.  If door requires key with number, key number will
be  printed  on  floor  near door.  Take care, generator is well surrounded
with  enemies.   After destroying it, proceed to landing point, marked with
big L.

        On  level  2  (3d  tunnel),  avoid  deadly  walls, which drain your
carrier  energy,  and  collect  as  much  as  possible  energy balls (extra
credits).

                             Enjoy this demo!

Use following keys:

        Arrow keys      - Movement
        Right Shift     - Fire
        Joystick        - Movement, Fire
        F1-F10          - Change weapons
        Space Bar       - Launch guided Missile
        M               - Map scanner mode (exit with M, Space, Esc, Fire)
        Help            - Activate NUKE (which must be collected on level)
        P               - Pause
        Esc             - Quit game

In the tunnel:

        Arrow keys      - Movement
        Joystick        - Movement
        P               - Pause
        Esc             - Abort level
